#Ex. 8 :- The function provided is broken. Your job is to figure out what's going on and fix it.

def append_greeting_to_name(name):
    # THIS IS BROKEN
    # YOUR JOB IS TO FIX IT
    # You can change this function as much as you want
    return "Hello" + name


Solution :- 

def append_greeting_to_name(name):
    return "Hello {}".format(name)
